        "conbody": {
            "p": [
                "You can select a specific source or sources in which to search. If there is a source you often search in, you can save that source as a favorite for future searches.",
                {
                    "uicontrol": [
                        {
                            "#tail": "at the top of the",
                            "#text": "Browse"
                        },
                        {
                            "#tail": ".  Then you can browse the sources by category, browse them alphabetically, or search for a specific source by name.",
                            "#text": "Sources"
                        }
                    ],
                    "ph": {
                        "@keyref": "prodnamefirst",
                        "#tail": "home page, then select"
                    },
                    "#text": "To select a specific source to search in, select"
                },
                "For more information about selecting sources, read through the links below."
            ],
            "note": {
                "uicontrol": [
                    {
                        "#tail": "after you have selected sources, your selections will replace the selections you made from",
                        "#text": "Filters"
                    },
                    {
                        "#tail": ".",
